data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in Flower Mound! This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence spans a generous 2,500 square feet of meticulously designed living space, offering the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Nestled in the prestigious Flower Mound High School district, this property promises an exceptional living experience for families seeking both academic excellence and a vibrant community.  The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring modern appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar. 
One of the highlights of this property is the backyard oasis, where a sparkling pool invites you to relax and unwind on warm Texas days. Imagine hosting barbecues, pool parties, and creating lasting memories in this private outdoor haven.
Convenience is key with this home, with its proximity to shopping, dining, and recreational opportunities. Enjoy the best of suburban living with easy access to major highways, making commuting a breeze.
